quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  54,7,"eyes downcast, they will come out of their graves like swarming locusts"
  54,8,"rushing towards the Summoner. The disbelievers will cry, ‘This is a stern day!’"
  54,9,"The people of Noah rejected the truth before them: they rejected Our servant, saying, ‘He is mad!’ Noah was rebuked,"
  54,10,"and so he called upon his Lord, ‘I am defeated: help me!’"